<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Polyamory&amp;action=edit&amp;section=28" title="Edit section: Polyamory-related media">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Polyamory-related media</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://polyinthemedia.blogspot.com" class="external text" title="http://polyinthemedia.blogspot.com" rel="nofollow">Polyamory in the News</a> website (a part of the <a href="http://www.polyamoryonline.org" class="external text" title="http://www.polyamoryonline.org" rel="nofollow">Polyamory Online</a> website).</li>
