<p><a name="Advocacy_and_awareness" id="Advocacy_and_awareness"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Polyamory&amp;action=edit&amp;section=30" title="Edit section: Advocacy and awareness">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Advocacy and awareness</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.uupa.org" class="external text" title="http://www.uupa.org" rel="nofollow">Unitarian Universalists for Polyamory Awareness</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.polyamory.org/~joe/polypaper.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.polyamory.org/~joe/polypaper.htm" rel="nofollow">What Psychology Professionals Should Know About Polyamory</a> A guide for mental health professionals which is favorable to polyamory.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.polychromatic.com/pfp/" class="external text" title="http://www.polychromatic.com/pfp/" rel="nofollow">Poly-Friendly Professionals</a> -- mental health and other professionals tolerant of or supportive of polyamory</li>
</ul>
